{"tid":597182,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中國公安衝上台！傳陳冠希商演突遭架走","createTime":"2018-03-18T11:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-18T11:31:13.000Z","uid":76009,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8a91abd3340ee5cd99f9a3bb9f813d07513554b3","tid":597182,"uid":76009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:20:15.000Z","msg":"中國公安衝上台！傳陳冠希商演突遭架走<br />\n<br />\n〔記者王心妤／台北報導〕香港男星陳冠希昨日在上海參加運動品牌活動，不料受訪到一半，突然有名男子衝上台直接喊：「走！帶了跑。」態度極像中國公安，直播也遭中斷，讓網友憂心陳冠希處境。<br />\n<br />\n據《蘋果日報》報導，陳冠希出席活動時大方接受媒體訪問，才上台說：「哈囉，大家好，我是陳冠希。」主持人接著問：「還開心嗎？」他又回：「還不錯啊！」就有名男子突衝進他與主持人中間將陳冠希推下台。之後傳出他是因「外籍人士沒有登記就進行商業演出」遭帶離現場，雖然陳冠希國際聯盟在微博發文表示「陳冠希已經平安離開。請各位粉絲不要擔心」，但香港經紀公司並未接電話。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/192003_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F192003_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e505dbbb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e640e7c8b611792d2e9c0619c4c41449b984869c","tid":597182,"uid":174074,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:22:44.000Z","msg":"一世都唔好番黎<br />\n人渣無用武之地"},{"pid":"cb84eb6703601bc96f458f03c3d24fb0d8180f06","tid":597182,"uid":51932,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:22:57.000Z","msg":"愛國要付出代價嘅，抵喇"},{"pid":"248306aa6943f4c5ea2be56388cea6497f5b79a0","tid":597182,"uid":28800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:23:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2acf963e28394a23f5a2dff3e1f9bf0896ab5e08","tid":597182,"uid":48905,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T11:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/18/192819_47753a2f8371a97fd1fe7dfee3c983a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F18%2F192819_47753a2f8371a97fd1fe7dfee3c983a4.png&h=f4743456&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee690632b3a46773ac4fb